org.knime.base.data.aggregation.dialogutil

Class ColumnAggregationTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • org.knime.base.data.aggregation.dialogutil.AbstractAggregationTableModel<AggregationMethod,NamedAggregationOperator>
        • org.knime.base.data.aggregation.dialogutil.ColumnAggregationTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, TableModel, AggregationTableModel<NamedAggregationOperator>

    public class ColumnAggregationTableModel
extends AbstractAggregationTableModel<AggregationMethod,NamedAggregationOperator>
    This DefaultTableModel holds all aggregation columns and their aggregation method. It is used in the Column Aggregator node which allows to specify a set of aggregation methods for a selected list of columns.
    Since:
    2.6
    Author:
    Tobias Koetter, University of Konstanz
